financial and operating results, the Company's plans, objectives, expectations and intentions and other statements that are not
historical facts. Forward-looking statements are neither historical facts nor assurances of future performance. Such statements are
based upon the beliefs and expectations of Clean Harbors' management as of this date only and are subject to certain risks and
