interest expense, loss on early extinguishment of debt and provision for income taxes and excludes other gains, losses and non-cash
charges not deemed representative of fundamental segment results and other expense (income), net. Transactions between the
segments are accounted for at the Company’s best estimate based on similar transactions with outside customers.
